strategies: I noticed some of the city names were real cities so I connected them to the other cities to better remember them.
familiar: I recalled the names of cities I have heard of and driven through in my life.
memorable: I thought about how easy it would be for me to search this city name if I ever had trouble remembering it.
unique: This could be somewhat related to uniness in certain aspects
realistic: if I am not entirely sure of how the city name is spelled but can recall it due to it's unique name.
similar: I thought about the names of cities I know about in real life and considered the likeliness of a city bearing each respective name.
